        <p>MEYERS--Nicholas, Music Supervisor and Editor for feature films and theatrical composer, died in the early morning hours of December 28, 2006 of complications from ALS. He was adored by his wife Sally Swisher, children Gabriel, Ada and Charlotte Meyers and his many friends. A memorial service will be announced.</p>
